  <brief_title>Soluble Dietary Fibres in the Prevention of Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Soluble Dietary Fibres as Dietetic Aid to Reduce the Risks of Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
